<h1>About Us</h1>

<p>Welcome to the Book Donors System!</p>

<p>This system is designed to make book donations simple, efficient, and transparent. Our mission is to connect donors with organizations in need and foster a community of knowledge sharing.</p>

<h2>Our Goals</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Encourage book donations and reduce book wastage.</li>
    <li>Provide an easy platform for donors to track their contributions.</li>
    <li>Support education and literacy initiatives globally.</li>
</ul>

